The paper is about a new dataset for recommender systems in the digital library and reference-management-software domain. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.IR (Information Retrieval). The paper also discusses the algorithms used to generate the recommendations, which could fall under cs.LG (Machine Learning) or cs.DB (Databases). The dataset also includes a range of recommendation data, which could be relevant to researchers in the fields of cs.CY (Computers and Society) and cs.DL (Digital Libraries).
